Subject: [PATCH] feat: polish Analytics page UI/UX + fix fake trend
 percentages

- Restyle MetricCard, ChartCard, TimeRangeSelector, and tables to match
  the premium dashboard look (rounded-2xl cards, soft icon backgrounds,
  hover states, indigo primary color)
- Reuse the shared EmptyState component from src/components/dashboard
- Replace hardcoded/fabricated trend percentages (Total Users +12.5%,
  Active Riders -3.2%, Success Rate +2.1%) with a real calcTrend()
  helper that compares first-half vs second-half of the fetched series
- Active Riders and Success Rate no longer show a trend badge, since
  the backend doesn't return time-series data to support one honestly
- No changes to API calls, endpoints, or business logic
